message: I propose a 90/10 split in my favor. Take it while it's still worth something!
Let's meet in the middle, 60-40 is a fair split.
The deal's getting worse for you, Bob. I'll offer 70/30. Time is money!
I'm willing to compromise, 55-45 is a good deal for both.
This is my final offer, Bob. 65/35 or I walk away. The clock is ticking!
